The paper also deals with noisy labels, which is a common problem in information theory, so cs.SI (Signal Processing) is also a possible sub-category. Finally, the paper proposes a new algorithm with a label complexity analysis, which is related to information theory and coding theory, so cs.IT (Information Theory) is also a possible sub-category.
